commit.message: Enable C++ tests in appveyor, only only Py2.7/3.7 64 bit for now.
Exclude a test from MSVC test runs that fails due to a linkage problem.
Fix test usage of overloaded C++ function in MSVC++.
Clarify usage of overloaded C++ function in MSVC++, which complains about its ambiguity.
Fix initialiser in C++ test: MSVC++ cannot assign statically to non-static members.
Avoid PyLong "L" suffix in test output on Windows.
Clarify types in atan2() call for usage in MSVC++.
